1
00:00:30,759 --> 00:00:34,080
Alien datang menaklukkan Bumi

2
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:36,839
Demi kakao yang dicari-cari

3
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:39,800
Mereka akan tiba tak lama lagi

4
00:00:39,879 --> 00:00:42,360
Apa mungkin terjadi?

5
00:00:42,919 --> 00:00:48,320
Jadi, kita memerlukan penyelamat Bumi

6
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:50,120
BoBoiBoy!

7
00:00:54,199 --> 00:00:56,160
BoBoiBoy!

8
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:02,000
BoBoiBoy!

9
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:03,320
MINUMAN DINGIN

10
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:05,679
Ying!

11
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,880
Yaya!

12
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:10,840
Gopal!

13
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:14,119
Dan pahlawan super kita

14
00:01:15,479 --> 00:01:17,160
BoBoiBoy!

15
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:23,160
BoBoiBoy!

16
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:33,000
BoBoiBoy!

17
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:37,640
Bapak dan Ibu.

18
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:40,360
Sebentar lagi, kita
akan sampai di stasiun berikutnya.

19
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:43,640
Terima kasih telah memilih
Yongpin Aerotrain.

20
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:46,080
Akhirnya sampai juga.

21
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:49,000
Aku tidak sabar untuk pergi karaoke.

22
00:01:49,559 --> 00:01:51,199
Harus pemanasan dahulu.

23
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:54,839
Wahai kupu-kupu

24
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,839
Terbanglah tinggi!

25
00:01:57,520 --> 00:02:00,080
Hei, Nak! Kau tidak boleh masuk ke sini!

26
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:03,039
Apa? Mikrofonnya masih menyala?

27
00:02:04,199 --> 00:02:05,399
Oh, tidak!

28
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:10,919
Saya minta maaf atas
kesalahan teknis yang terjadi.

29
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:14,160
Terima kasih,
tolong jangan beri tahu atasan saya.

30
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,600
Bagus!

31
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,440
Aku bisa ceritakan ke Kakek.

32
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,760
Akhirnya, kita sampai di sektor terakhir.

33
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:35,359
Bagus. Mulai pencarian.

34
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,079
Pencarian dimulai.

35
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:42,280
Data pencarian menunjukkan tenaga
yang tinggi dari salah satu planet.

36
00:02:42,359 --> 00:02:43,359
Planet mana?

37
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,440
Planet Bumi!

38
00:02:44,519 --> 00:02:46,280
Planet Bumi?

39
00:02:46,359 --> 00:02:47,760
Kecepatan penuh!

40
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:51,000
Perhatian! Kereta akan segera datang…

41
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:53,079
Sudah tidak sabar bertemu cucuku.

42
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:56,400
Tolong berdiri di belakang garis kuning
demi keselamatan Anda.

43
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,920
Terima kasih sudah menemaniku.

44
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,480
Sama-sama. Salam, ya, untuk Tok Aba.

45
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,760
Jangan nakal.

46
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,400
- Sampai jumpa!
- Sampai jumpa!

47
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:08,920
Sudah tidak sabar bertemu Kakek!

48
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,519
BoBoiBoy!

49
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:16,600
Kakek!

50
00:03:16,679 --> 00:03:18,239
BoBoiBoy!

51
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:23,880
Cucu Kakek sudah besar.

52
00:03:23,959 --> 00:03:24,920
Kakek?

53
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,120
Ya?

54
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:28,079
Aku bukan BoBoiBoy.

55
00:03:29,359 --> 00:03:31,880
Wah, Kakek kelihatan lebih muda!

56
00:03:32,679 --> 00:03:35,760
Kau memeluk siapa?

57
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:39,840
Maaf, Pak.

58
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,359
Kakek juga sama.

59
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,440
Kakek juga sama!

60
00:03:44,519 --> 00:03:47,560
Bukan salah Kakek. Kakek sudah tua.

61
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,519
Kau masih muda, tapi sudah lupa.

62
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,679
Kakek, apa kabar?

63
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:54,119
Baik. Ayo kita pulang.

64
00:03:55,119 --> 00:03:58,079
Kakek, tadi masinis kereta
lupa mematikan mikrofon.

65
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,839
Benarkah?

66
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,839
Bapak ini siapa?

67
00:04:06,359 --> 00:04:09,359
Bos, jenis tenaga yang terdeteksi
adalah yang terkuat.

68
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,280
Tenaga kakao.

69
00:04:10,359 --> 00:04:12,399
Apa? Tenaga kakao?

70
00:04:15,239 --> 00:04:16,320
Bos tidak tahu?

71
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:18,640
Aku tahu, tapi lupa.

72
00:04:18,719 --> 00:04:21,479
Kakao merupakan jenis tenaga yang terkuat.

73
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,760
Tenaga ini dipercayai sudah punah.

74
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:27,200
Apa? Kita harus mendapatkan tenaga ini!

75
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,400
Komputer! Nyalakan lampu!

76
00:04:30,039 --> 00:04:32,000
Tampilkan gambar planet Bumi.

77
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:38,200
Aku tahu kenapa banyak
tenaga kakao di sini.

78
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:41,240
Lihat! Tidak ada
makhluk yang tinggal di planet ini!

79
00:04:42,599 --> 00:04:44,719
Itu bulan, bukan Bumi.

80
00:04:45,919 --> 00:04:46,760
Aku tahu.

81
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:48,039
Ya, tapi bohong.

82
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,200
Diam!

83
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:52,440
Komputer!
Cari informasi tentang kakao di Bumi!

84
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,080
Baik, Bos!

85
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,880
Kita sudah sampai. Turun.

86
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:06,479
Wah, rumahnya tua.

87
00:05:07,479 --> 00:05:08,919
Tua seperti Kakek.

88
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:13,039
Cucu nakal. Kau masih sempat meledek?

89
00:05:13,919 --> 00:05:15,240
Sudah, masuk.

90
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,800
Meskipun tua, rumahnya masih kokoh.

91
00:05:19,599 --> 00:05:21,800
Sama seperti yang punya.

92
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,400
Iya, Tok Aba.

93
00:05:23,479 --> 00:05:25,120
Ini kamarmu.

94
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:31,120
Kakek yang menyiapkan semuanya?

95
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,960
Iya. Memang siapa lagi?

96
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,159
Lumayan untuk ditempati.

97
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,200
Lagi pula, kau tak akan lama di sini.

98
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,840
Wah, luar biasa!

99
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,560
Kakek senang kau ke sini.

100
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:50,640
Kakek butuh bantuan karena sudah tua.

101
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,919
Mau diminta tolong, malah tidur.

102
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:58,200
Anak ini malah tidur
saat aku sedang bicara.

103
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,800
BoBoiBoy, bangun.

104
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:07,919
Kasihan, cucu Kakek lelah. Tidur nyenyak.

105
00:06:08,479 --> 00:06:11,120
Tampaknya penduduk Bumi
menggunakan kakao sebagai makanan.

106
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:13,760
Apa? Mereka makan kakao?

107
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:17,440
Mereka tidak tahu
kalau kakao adalah tenaga yang terkuat.

108
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:20,000
Kau juga baru tahu tadi.

109
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:20,919
Diam!

110
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,760
Turun ke Bumi dan buat pengumuman!

111
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:27,520
Aku akan memaksa
penduduk bumi untuk menyerahkan kakao!

112
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:32,159
Tok Aba!

113
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:35,240
Tok Aba ke mana, ya?

114
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,080
Di mana?

115
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,799
"Bertemu di kedai Tok Aba?"

116
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:54,400
Baiklah. Kunci pintu? Sudah!

117
00:06:54,479 --> 00:06:56,400
Sekarang, menyapa Yaya.

118
00:06:56,479 --> 00:06:58,680
Jadi, dia seperti ini?

119
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,560
"Yaya?"

120
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:01,680
Hai, BoBoiBoy!

121
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:06,760
Kau ini. Mengagetkan saja.

122
00:07:08,039 --> 00:07:10,000
Bagaimana kau tahu namaku?

123
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:11,640
Oh, Tok Aba yang memberi tahu.

124
00:07:11,719 --> 00:07:13,320
Tok Aba memang suka begitu.

125
00:07:14,799 --> 00:07:17,760
Oh, Tok Aba bilang,
terima kasih untuk biskuit semalam.

126
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,200
Sama-sama!

127
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:21,400
Tok Aba pasti suka biskuitnya, 'kan?

128
00:07:21,479 --> 00:07:23,320
Tidak tahu. Mungkin saja.

129
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,880
Baiklah, Yaya. Aku mau pergi
ke kedai Tok Aba.

130
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,719
- Kedai Tok Aba?
- Ya.

131
00:07:27,799 --> 00:07:30,719
Oh, mudah. Belok kanan, lalu…

132
00:07:30,799 --> 00:07:33,840
Oh, tidak perlu.
Tok Aba sudah menulisnya di kertas ini.

133
00:07:33,919 --> 00:07:36,520
- Sampai jumpa!
- Sampai jumpa.

134
00:07:36,599 --> 00:07:40,039
Baiklah. Pertama, turuni tangga
di dekat rumah.

135
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:43,479
Lalu seberangi jalan,
tapi jangan lupa tengok kanan dan kiri.

136
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:47,239
Turun tangga sekali lagi,
tapi hati-hati karena ada turunan!

137
00:07:48,359 --> 00:07:50,280
Ada banyak anjing.

138
00:07:50,359 --> 00:07:53,000
Nanti, kau akan sampai di ladang karet.

139
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:55,919
Setelah itu, lurus sampai ke pantai.

140
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,080
Setelah itu, lurus saja.

141
00:08:00,159 --> 00:08:04,200
Lurus saja sampai melihat kedai Tok Aba.

142
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,080
Akhirnya sampai juga!

143
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,320
Lelah sekali.

144
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:12,239
Bagaimana Tok Aba bisa
berjalan kaki ke sini setiap hari?

145
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,520
Kasihan Tok Aba.

146
00:08:13,599 --> 00:08:15,159
Jangan khawatir.

147
00:08:15,239 --> 00:08:18,000
Kakek naik motor.
Lagi pula, dekat dari rumah.

148
00:08:23,679 --> 00:08:26,880
Kenapa aku harus jalan sejauh itu?

149
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:29,359
Kenapa? Supaya kau sedikit berolahraga.

150
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,159
Kekek memang usil.

151
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,480
Hai, BoBoiBoy!

152
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,319
Jauh, ya?

153
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:41,520
Karena itu, aku mau
menunjukkan jalannya tadi.

154
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:44,000
Bukan tak mau, tapi aku masih malu, Mimi.

155
00:08:44,079 --> 00:08:46,760
Mimi? Aku Yaya!

156
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:49,360
Benarkah? Aku kira Mimi.

157
00:08:49,439 --> 00:08:53,199
Aku ingat namamu,
tapi kau tak ingat namaku.

158
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,480
Sudah, kalian berdua jangan bertengkar.

159
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:57,920
Nanti tidak ada yang datang ke sini.

160
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,199
Ini kedai apa?

161
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:06,840
Kedai kakekmu sendiri tidak tahu?

162
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,560
Kau siapa?

163
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,959
Tenang. Akan aku jelaskan.

164
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:14,760
Inilah Kedai Kakao Tok Aba!

165
00:09:14,839 --> 00:09:16,199
Tok Aba, dia siapa?

166
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:20,000
- Gopal. Selalu minta produk gratis.
- Dia menyediakan makanan dan minuman.

167
00:09:20,079 --> 00:09:21,560
Yang terbuat dari kakao!

168
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,040
Ada kue cokelat!

169
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,240
Es krim cokelat!

170
00:09:24,319 --> 00:09:25,480
Pisang goreng cokelat!

171
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:27,400
Dan yang terbaik,

172
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,920
cokelat panas spesial Tok Aba!

173
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,199
COKELAT PANAS TOK ABA

174
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:33,120
Ada yang salah dengan anak ini.

175
00:09:33,199 --> 00:09:36,800
Tok Aba hanya menjanjikan
yang terbaik dengan motonya,

176
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:38,160
"Dijamin puas!"

177
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:40,360
Jadilah pelanggan setia seperti saya

178
00:09:40,439 --> 00:09:43,520
dan nikmati potongan harga
sampai 100 persen!

179
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,319
Sejak kapan?

180
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,520
Kakek tak pernah bilang!

181
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,640
Hai.

182
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,680
Aku BoBoiBoy.

183
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:53,640
Gopal! Teman baikmu!

184
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:57,959
Tok Aba, saya sudah jadi teman baiknya.
Boleh minta cokelat panas gratis?

185
00:10:00,959 --> 00:10:02,920
Apa? Aku cuma bertanya.

186
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,920
BoBoiBoy, angkat teleponnya!

187
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:07,959
Halo?

188
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,240
Halo, Tok Aba!

189
00:10:09,319 --> 00:10:11,199
Ini bukan Tok Aba.

190
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,480
Ini BoBoiBoy?

191
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,280
Ya.

192
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:17,160
Aku Ying!

193
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,560
Aku mau pesan minuman.

194
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:21,160
Boleh. Mau pesan apa?

195
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,760
Satu cokelat panas spesial!

196
00:10:22,839 --> 00:10:25,400
Baiklah! Tok Aba,
satu cokelat panas spesial!

197
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:27,360
Aku minum di sini.

198
00:10:27,439 --> 00:10:28,760
Minum di sini!

199
00:10:28,839 --> 00:10:29,720
Baiklah.

200
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,680
Terima kasih!

201
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,680
Sama-sama.

202
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:37,520
Ying, kenapa kau tidak pesan langsung?

203
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,760
Aku malu.

204
00:10:39,839 --> 00:10:42,240
Abaikan saja. Dia memang seperti itu.

205
00:10:42,319 --> 00:10:43,280
Kita menonton TV saja.

206
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,360
Penduduk Bumi!

207
00:10:55,439 --> 00:10:59,240
Aku adalah Adu Du dari planet Ata Ta Tiga!

208
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:04,640
Serahkan semua biji kakao kalian,
atau bersiaplah untuk musnah…

209
00:11:05,199 --> 00:11:06,800
Kenapa kau ganti saluran?

210
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:08,920
Karena membosankan.

211
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,199
Tidak!

212
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:13,000
Mereka mengira
pengumuman tadi adalah acara TV!

213
00:11:13,079 --> 00:11:15,120
Bagaimana bisa?

214
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:20,640
Tuan Bos, aku telah mengumpulkan info
tentang penduduk Bumi.

215
00:11:20,719 --> 00:11:23,000
Hasilnya sungguh menakutkan!

216
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:25,160
Apa yang menakutkan?

217
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,120
Lihat ini, Tuan Bos!

218
00:11:28,199 --> 00:11:31,600
Lihat apa yang mereka lakukan
terhadap makhluk hijau!

219
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:34,079
Mereka memotong
makhluk hijau menjadi kecil,

220
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:36,600
lalu mereka masak di dalam air mendidih!

221
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,640
Dan akhirnya,

222
00:11:38,719 --> 00:11:43,199
mereka memaksa
anak-anak memakannya sampai habis!

223
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:48,640
Kenapa mereka sangat kejam
kepada makhluk hijau seperti aku?

224
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:51,199
Untung aku ungu.

225
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:53,880
Pantas mereka tidak takut
pada pengumuman kita.

226
00:11:53,959 --> 00:11:56,280
Sepertinya kita tidak punya pilihan lain.

227
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:58,719
Kita harus menggunakan Bola Kekuatan!

228
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:02,160
Tapi Bola Kekuatan memerlukan

229
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:04,360
tenaga yang besar untuk diaktifkan!

230
00:12:04,439 --> 00:12:07,520
Aku tahu. Kita akan menggunakan
tenaga kakao!

231
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:10,079
Probe! Pergilah dan curi kakao itu!

232
00:12:10,959 --> 00:12:12,560
Kenapa harus aku, Tuan Bos?

233
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:14,600
Karena kau berwarna ungu.

234
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:17,040
Kenapa aku dilahirkan berwarna ungu?

235
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:20,079
Baiklah, BoBoiBoy. Kakek mau pergi.
Jaga kedainya sebentar.

236
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:22,560
Aku tidak tahu harus apa.

237
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,640
Bagaimana kalau ada banyak pelanggan?

238
00:12:24,719 --> 00:12:26,839
Jangan takut. Mereka cuma orang.

239
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:28,360
Bukan alien.

240
00:12:28,439 --> 00:12:29,280
Sampai nanti!

241
00:12:31,839 --> 00:12:33,280
Tok Aba ada-ada saja.

242
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,319
Kalau alien datang, aku harus apa?

243
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:47,800
Hampir saja!

244
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:55,240
Astaga!

245
00:12:55,319 --> 00:12:57,240
Mereka juga memakan alien ungu!

246
00:12:59,000 --> 00:12:59,880
Pencuri!

247
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:01,839
Jangan lari!

248
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:05,640
Jangan makan aku! Aku tidak enak!

249
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:14,040
Berhenti!

250
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:22,560
Habislah aku.

251
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:24,199
Tok Aba pasti marah.

252
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:28,959
Makhluk apa yang mencuri kakao tadi?

253
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:36,599
Masuk ke mana dia?

254
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:42,079
Tuan Bos! Aku berhasil mencuri kakao!

255
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,560
Bagus!

256
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,920
Terima kasih. Aku memang…

257
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:48,079
Apa salahku?

258
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:50,319
Kau memberikan informasi yang salah!

259
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:52,599
Penduduk Bumi tidak memakan makhluk hijau.

260
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:55,480
Gambar yang kau ambil tadi
adalah gambar sayuran.

261
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:58,880
Berhenti!

262
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:02,400
Kau mau pergi ke mana?

263
00:14:04,199 --> 00:14:06,280
Aku akan mengembalikan kakao ini.

264
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:09,000
Kenapa kau mau mengembalikan kakao itu?

265
00:14:09,079 --> 00:14:10,000
Bawa ke sini!

266
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:15,240
Iya, penduduk Bumi tidak ganas.

267
00:14:15,319 --> 00:14:17,880
Jadi, kita tak perlu kakao
untuk mengaktifkan Bola Kekuatan.

268
00:14:17,959 --> 00:14:19,400
Komputer, pukul dia!

269
00:14:19,479 --> 00:14:20,520
Baik, Bos.

270
00:14:25,839 --> 00:14:27,040
Kau bodoh!

271
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:30,520
Ini kesempatan kita
untuk mengaktifkan Bola Kekuatan

272
00:14:30,599 --> 00:14:32,120
dengan tenaga kakao!

273
00:14:32,199 --> 00:14:34,880
Dengan Bola Kekuatan,
kita akan menguasai Bumi

274
00:14:34,959 --> 00:14:37,760
dan merampas semua kakao!

275
00:14:37,839 --> 00:14:39,719
Sakit.

276
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:42,560
Sudah! Ikuti aku ke ruang senjata.

277
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:47,360
Itu alien yang tadi ada di TV.

278
00:15:03,079 --> 00:15:05,760
Komputer, masukkan kakao itu sekarang.

279
00:15:05,839 --> 00:15:07,319
Baik, Bos.

280
00:15:25,599 --> 00:15:26,560
Bagus!

281
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:28,280
Dengan tenaga kakao,

282
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:31,280
Bola Kekuatan akan dapat diaktifkan!

283
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:33,760
Jadi, itu cara mereka mendapat tenaga.

284
00:15:33,839 --> 00:15:35,599
Aku harus mengambil kakao itu.

285
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:39,439
Bos, Bola Kekuatan
memerlukan sedikit waktu untuk aktif.

286
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:40,520
Apa?

287
00:15:40,599 --> 00:15:42,959
Aku ingin melihat kekuatannya sekarang!

288
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:45,439
Apa?

289
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:50,000
Komputer, masukkan kakao itu
ke dalam Probe.

290
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:51,599
Baik, Bos.

291
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:55,280
Bagaimana, Probe? Apa yang kau rasakan?

292
00:15:56,319 --> 00:15:58,880
Aku merasa…

293
00:15:58,959 --> 00:16:00,120
kakao ini lezat!

294
00:16:00,199 --> 00:16:01,079
Apa?

295
00:16:13,479 --> 00:16:14,359
Probe!

296
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:21,599
Bos, Probe memasuki laboratorium.

297
00:16:22,959 --> 00:16:24,760
Komputer, nyalakan lampu sekarang!

298
00:16:33,599 --> 00:16:35,400
Aku Super Probe!

299
00:16:35,479 --> 00:16:37,000
Robot pemusnah!

300
00:16:45,439 --> 00:16:47,120
Sudah cukup!

301
00:16:47,199 --> 00:16:48,040
Alah.

302
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:49,280
Apa?

303
00:16:49,359 --> 00:16:51,040
Kalau pesawat ini meledak, kau mau ganti?

304
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:53,560
Bos, Bola Kekuatan telah diaktifkan!

305
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:56,000
Bagus! Ayo ikut aku.

306
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:03,880
Bos.

307
00:17:05,919 --> 00:17:08,079
Dengan Bola Kekuatan dan Super Probe,

308
00:17:08,639 --> 00:17:09,879
kita pasti akan…

309
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:13,960
Hai

310
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:15,319
Hanya lewat.

311
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:17,839
Bos! Itu Bola Kekuatan!

312
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:20,240
Probe, kejar dia!

313
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,919
Komputer, tutup semua pintu masuk!

314
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:37,520
Tuan Bos?

315
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:06,720
Bos, anak itu berhasil kabur
dengan Bola Kekuatan!

316
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:09,600
Bodoh! Cari dia sampai dapat!

317
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,919
Cari!

318
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:14,960
Ke mana saja kau, BoBoiBoy?

319
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:16,200
Kau membuat Kakek khawatir!

320
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:18,240
Tadi, aku mengejar alien.

321
00:18:18,320 --> 00:18:19,639
Dia mencuri kakao ini.

322
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:21,280
Waktu mau mengambilnya kembali,

323
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:23,600
ada robot besar yang mengejarku!

324
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,760
Kau kebanyakan makan cokelat.

325
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:29,040
Tok Aba tidak mendengarkan ceritaku?

326
00:18:29,120 --> 00:18:30,520
Kakek dengar.

327
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:31,679
Sudah, ayo pulang.

328
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:34,480
Kakek mau tutup kedainya.

329
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:40,639
Tok Aba tidak percaya ceritaku.

330
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:44,159
Bola, bagaimana cara membuat
Tok Aba percaya?

331
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,440
Aku tahu!

332
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:47,320
Ochobot!

333
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:50,000
Astaga!

334
00:18:50,080 --> 00:18:51,520
Aduh.

335
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:53,679
Kau ini…

336
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:55,159
Kau Bola Kekuatan Adu Du!

337
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:57,000
Adu Du?

338
00:18:57,080 --> 00:18:58,399
Namaku Ochobot!

339
00:18:58,480 --> 00:19:00,320
Kau mau apa dari aku? Katakan!

340
00:19:00,399 --> 00:19:02,800
Aku ingin memberimu kekuatan!

341
00:19:02,879 --> 00:19:04,320
Kekuatan?

342
00:19:04,399 --> 00:19:05,879
Ya. Kekuatan.

343
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:11,360
Bos, aku mendeteksi
sebuah gelombang tenaga yang kuat.

344
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:13,320
Itu pasti dari Bola Kekuatan!

345
00:19:13,399 --> 00:19:14,560
Cari lokasinya!

346
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:19,919
Wah! Apa ini?

347
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,919
Itu jam kekuatanmu!

348
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,720
Kenapa kau memberi ini padaku?

349
00:19:25,879 --> 00:19:27,600
Bukankah kau yang mengaktifkan aku?

350
00:19:28,919 --> 00:19:30,560
Benar!

351
00:19:30,639 --> 00:19:32,120
Jadi, apa kekuatanku?

352
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:37,639
Kekuatan Elemen!

353
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:40,679
Kau bisa mengendalikan elemen
yang ada di planet ini!

354
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:41,760
Benarkah?

355
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:43,720
Bagaimana cara menggunakannya?

356
00:19:43,800 --> 00:19:44,639
Sabar!

357
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:47,560
Untuk menggunakan kekuatan ini,
kau harus banyak berlatih.

358
00:19:47,639 --> 00:19:50,879
Karena kekuatanmu itu
paling sulit dikendalikan.

359
00:19:57,560 --> 00:20:00,720
Kau berhasil menggunakan Elemen Petir!

360
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:02,280
Bagaimana kau melakukannya?

361
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:04,440
Seperti ini.

362
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:08,000
Tidak terjadi apa-apa.

363
00:20:08,080 --> 00:20:09,879
Bagaimana cara melakukannya?

364
00:20:12,679 --> 00:20:14,240
Panas!

365
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:21,440
Sepertinya akan hujan lebat.

366
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:23,159
Hebat!

367
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:24,480
Elemen Angin!

368
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:27,040
Bagus!

369
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:29,560
BoBoiBoy, tutup jendelamu!

370
00:20:29,639 --> 00:20:31,240
Astaga! Tok Aba!

371
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:33,120
Bagaimana ini?

372
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:37,919
BoBoiBoy! Gempa bumi!

373
00:20:38,919 --> 00:20:40,399
Gempa bumi apa, Kakek?

374
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:44,320
Sudah. Tutup jendelamu.

375
00:20:44,399 --> 00:20:45,639
Akan segera hujan.

376
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:47,159
Baik, Kakek!

377
00:20:48,679 --> 00:20:50,159
Untung tidak ketahuan!

378
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:54,879
Sekarang, aku adalah pahlawan super!

379
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:57,000
Kau sudah menggunakan Elemen Tanah!

380
00:20:58,399 --> 00:21:00,000
Gempa bumi!

381
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:12,679
Jangan takut pada langit yang gelap

382
00:21:12,760 --> 00:21:17,240
Ayo, beranikan diri saja

383
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:22,560
Kita hadapi semua bersama

384
00:21:22,639 --> 00:21:25,600
Marilah

385
00:21:25,679 --> 00:21:29,040
Kita bertualang

386
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:32,120
Inilah saatnya

387
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:36,000
Untuk bersenang-senang

388
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:39,080
Jangan bimbang

389
00:21:39,159 --> 00:21:42,520
Jangan ragu

390
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:45,639
Pasti mengagumkan

391
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:49,520
Biar ia bawa kau pergi

392
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:52,399
Bersiaplah

393
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:55,800
Ayo bertualang

394
00:21:55,879 --> 00:21:59,560
Ini saatnya

395
00:21:59,639 --> 00:22:02,520
Bersiaplah

396
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:05,439
Bersiaplah

397
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:07,919
Terjemahan subtitle oleh
Fitriyadi Sulistiyono

